  <brief_title>Operative Treatment of Extraarticular Colles' Fractures of the Distal Radius (OTEC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective, Randomized, Multi-Center Pilot Study on the Treatment of Unstable, Extraarticular Colles Fractures of the Distal Radius by Palmar Locking Plate, External Fixator or Kirschner Wires</official_title>
